# loadFolderById

Retrieve one folder by its ID.

## Usage

```js
await connector.runOS({
  method: SYSTEM_CALL.loadFolderById,
  params: folderId,
});
```

## Parameters

- `folderId`: `string` - The ID of the folder to load.

## Returns

```
StructuredFolders
```
